{"tid":2081840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣佈： 以後唔撚捐血！","createTime":"2020-06-27T14:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T16:55:38.000Z","uid":167559,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2dced776898c6d5a15c9b5f5be1c8b97695e09f1","tid":2081840,"uid":167559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">【警隊玻璃心】警察藍絲群組狙擊涉事抽血員 po相起底兼留言「黑暴女主角」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網傳一批警務人員23日在九龍灣輔警總部捐血時，因有抽血員佩戴寫有「黑警死全家」等字眼的飾物，要求紅十字會提供該抽血員名字及職銜被拒絕，最終腰斬捐血活動。不過有消息指，該名抽血員當日只是佩戴了迷你黃色頭盔掛飾，並無涉及任何侮辱性字眼。藍絲群組繼續狙擊該抽血員，於facebook群組上載懷疑是該名抽血員的相片，並留言形容「黑暴女主角」，「大家一於齊齊推爆捧紅佢」，有關相片截圖最早是於警察群組<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span>中流傳。<br />\n<br />\n紅十字會輸血服務中心23日到九龍灣輔警總部舉行捐血日，網上流傳有來自醫管局的抽血人員佩戴寫有「黑警死全家」、「對抗警暴」等字眼的飾物，惹在場警員不滿，警方要求紅十字會提供相關人員名字及職銜被拒絕，最終腰斬捐血活動。不過有消息指該名抽血員其實當日只是佩戴了迷你黃色頭盔掛飾，並無涉及任何侮辱性字眼。紅十字會及食衞局卻先後跪低。<br />\n<br />\n藍絲群組繼續狙擊該抽血員，於fb群組上載懷疑是該名抽血員的相片，並留言「紅十字會去輔警總部，刻意侮辱捐血的輔警，此就是黑暴女主角，大家一於齊齊推爆捧紅佢」，似想製造網上欺凌。據了解，有關相片截圖最早是於警察群組中流傳。<br />\n<br />\n事件發生後紅十字會fb專頁留言有逾6,000個對該事件的留言，如「一個鎖匙扣令貴會這樣反應，我不會再捐錢和血」、「點解要道歉 工作人員做錯乜」、「失專業既（嘅）係警察 」。不少網民不忿警方「玻璃心」，批評紅十字會未調查清楚事件便道歉，甚至揚言不會再捐血。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200627/B3XBJXVBWSRPGFHETACDI6OPGA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200627%2FB3XBJXVBWSRPGFHETACDI6OPGA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=5d6f7168\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200627%2FB3XBJXVBWSRPGFHETACDI6OPGA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=ffe5e4da\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200627/B3XBJXVBWSRPGFHETACDI6OPGA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"424d1cf8bbc34d38f05529f9f56f4bbc9e895667","tid":2081840,"uid":231583,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:06:32.000Z","msg":"本身就唔應該捐血，繼續呼籲d未醒既人唔好再捐"},{"pid":"f1056fbb49f4f743819ff0d0e31fb5b240d2bbf5","tid":2081840,"uid":214502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:06:48.000Z","msg":"叫藍血人捐飽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9e0c5eddebc3bbbf855584f64dad168e85f54a","tid":2081840,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:06:52.000Z","msg":"就算佢唔跪底都唔捐架啦<br />\n使撚你宣佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ddbd2865527a831dda7f25c6aa24db11aabe54","tid":2081840,"uid":62891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:07:23.000Z","msg":"本身唔捐"},{"pid":"ff54f8c63dcb4075bad0bb07def7549de308a102","tid":2081840,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d59470535aab92ddc54819e7dc9b16fb77a32aa","tid":2081840,"uid":240890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:07:55.000Z","msg":"入去紅十字個fb page 洗爆佢"},{"pid":"15dd5c9301890e58f5ae9de0b13d3dc7c82dabc4","tid":2081840,"uid":199223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:09:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e3fb7ae488bd310dc040c39d3a8ffeef072bd41","tid":2081840,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:09:40.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"53f996a053f0f10255c68d3a7dd505ef27df59f6","tid":2081840,"uid":191588